description:
Any documents that consist of 

1. summary or reports of your office's research into the proposed merger of Anthem, Inc. and Cigna Corp.;
2. recommendation of your office's staff to its attorney general on how to proceed with the above-referenced merger case;
3. requests for documents or information your office sent to to Anthem, Inc. or Cigna Corp;
4. contracts between your state and any subject matter experts for the purpose of assisting your office's work on the above-referenced merger case;
5. correspondence between your office and the U.S. Department of Justice Antitrust Division regarding the above-referenced merger case.
